ith active play.} Rg8 {[%cal Gg8g2]} 28. Rd2 a3 29. b4 {Forced, as otherwise, White's position collapses.} f5 {Stopping [f5] ideas.} 30. exf5 Bxf5 $15 {[%csl Ga3,Gf5,Ge7] With a crazy position. Two bishops and the [a3]-pawn give us enough compensation.} *

