ple:} 25. Qf3 e4 (25... e4 {The idea is to meet} 26. Rxe4 {with} Qc5 $1 {and we will win back the pawn soon thanks to the ...[Qc1]+ threat.}) 26. Qxf5 exf5 {The material balance is in White's favour but we have clearly better pieces.} 27. g4 {This can be met with dynamic chess.} e3 28. gxf5 Rxf5 29. Re2 Bh4 $10 {With an equal position.} *

