e pretends nothing is happening and goes} 21. a7 {, we'll remind them that things are really happening!} Nf5 22. Qd2 d4 {and ...[d3] followed by ...[Rc2] could be next, for instance. ...[Qb6] and ...[e3] is also an idea.}) *

