 Rxb2 $1 {[%csl Rc1,Ra3] This is our idea.} 21. Kxb2 {This is losing.} Qxa3+ 22. Kc2 Qxa2+ 23. Kc1 e4 $1 {[%csl Rc1,Gc8] The idea is to cut off the queen from the defence. If White captures the e-pawn, then ...[Rc8] becomes possible.} 24. Rxd6 Qa3+ {[%cal Ga3c1,Ga3d6]} 25. Kc2 Qxd6 {Winning back material and leaving White with a terribly exposed king.} *

