 endgame where some precise moves from our side will be required.} e4 19. Bxb5 Qxf5 20. Qxf5 Bxf5 21. Bd7 {It makes sense to exchange one of the bishops and try to put some pressure in the endgame with active rooks. However, after a few precise moves, we should not face any serious trouble.} Bxd7 22. Rxd7 Bxb2 23. Nc4 Bg7 24. Rfd1 {Now I believe I found the easiest way to achieve draw.} Rab8 {This has never been tried in an over-the-board game.} 25. Ra7 Rb4 {[%csl Rc4][%cal Gb4a4] The point! We are in time to save the pawn.} *

