he rook trade.} 24. Rxf4 exf4 25. e5 Qf5 {with an interesting position. Looks like White cannot save both central pawns because the knight is too far away. ...[f3] is a threat, so White needs to think about how to deal with it.}) 22... exf4 23. Nc2 Re8 {[%cal Gd6g6] With a good activity. The knight has slightly improved but is still struggling to find a good square.} *

