o late for king's evacuation.} Rad8 15. Qa3 Bg5+ 16. Kb1 Rxd1+ 17. Nxd1 Rd8 {White is still struggling to consolidate.} 18. Be2 {White gets again under attack.} Nd4 $1 {[%csl Re2,Rc4,Rf3] With a decisive advantage for Black.} *

