ion and allows Black to get a preferable position.} Rxc1 18. Rxc1 Nxb3 19. axb3 Qd8 {[%cal Gf8e8,Gb7c6] It's time to untangle. ...[Bc6] and ...[Re8] will follow next, and we are still a pawn up.} *

