e the knight's position by heading to [f5].} c4 {I like going for immediate counterplay.} 16. Ne3 cxd3 $1 17. cxd3 Be6 {[%cal Ga8d8,Gg7h5,Gh5f4] Now we have a target on [d3] which we can further press with ...[Rd8] and we can even try to bring the knight to [f4] via [h5].} *

