the e-file, we can simply prevent the knight jump. The immediate} 16. Nb5 {could be met with} Qf6 {followed by ...[a6].}) 16... a6 $1 {[%cal Ga6b5,Ge2e5,Ga8e8] Preventing [Nb5] ideas for once and for all and planning to consolidate with ...[Re8].} 17. Bd2 ({Now Qxe5 is a real threat, but the immediate} 17. Qxe5 $4 {would be a nice gift for us!} Re8 {-+}) 17... Re8 {[%csl Gd7,Ge5,Gf5,Gf8] Black has a comfortable position with two bishops and a nice pawn chain controlling the central squares thus limiting White's options.} *

