oo much and is met by} Qd7 {with ...[Nd4] ideas.}) ({We can meet} 11. h5 {with} h6 {.}) 11... Bxh4 {White gives a pawn hoping to get enough compensation.} 12. Nf5 {Forcing the exchange.} Bxf5 13. exf5 Ne7 {Black's best, seeking to exchange the powerful white knight.} 14. g4 Nxd5 15. Qxd5 Qe7 {[%cal Ge8c8,Gh4g5] White has some compensation but nothing more.} *

