]} 17. f5 Ng5 {This has a funny look, but this is very solid for Black!} 18. h4 {That's simply too much.} Ngh7 {[%cal Ge7f8,Gd5d4,Gc8b7] Black is taking over. White pushed their pawns too far and weakened themselves.} *

