1. e4 c5 2. a3 {[%cal Gb2b4] Generally a blitz weapon at the highest level and has been played by none others than Carlsen, Nepo or Mamedyarov!} g6 {[%cal Gg7a1] Exactly the same concept as against 2.b3. We don't want White to occupy the diagonal [a1]-[h8].} 3. Nc3 {White is changing their plans to play a Grand Prix Attack almost a tempo down as [a3] is not completely useless. The light-squared bishop will certainly be safe on [a2]!} Bg7 4. Bc4 (4. g3 {doesn’t make any sense; now, it is really a Closed Sicilian one tempo down for White after} Nc6 {.}) 4... Nc6 5. d3 e6 {[%cal Gc4e6]} 6. Ba2 {A useful waiting move asking Black where they want to develop the [g8]-knight.} d6 $1 ({And we don’t answer! We just play a useful move returning White the favour. Quite a rare move, but I think it is clever.} 6... Nge7 7. h4 $5 {is exactly what White wants.}) 7. Be3 {[%cal Gd1d2]} (7. h4 Nf6 $1 {is the main point of not playing 7...Nge7. Now, it will be very difficult for White to justify the early [h4] push.} 8. Nge2 O-O {Even this is completely fine; Black will soon strike in the centre with ...[d5].}) 7... Nf6 {[%cal Ge8g8,Gf6h5,Gd6d5] The knight is doing a great job on [f6] defending against a possible [h4]-[h5]. Sometimes, ...[Ng4] can happen and, of course, the knight supports a possible central break such as ...[d5].} 8. Qd2 {[%cal Ge3h6]} O-O {Not being afraid of ghosts.} 9. Bh6 b5 {Our counterattack is very fast!} 10. h4 ({After} 10. Nxb5 Rb8 {, we are immediately getting back our pawn and infiltrating White's camp. That's not an acceptable outcome for White.}) 10... Bxh6 $1 11. Qxh6 Nd4 {[%cal Gd4c2]} 12. Rc1 Rb8 {[%cal Gb5b4,Gf6g4] White's attack is not really dangerous as the Queen can be kicked out of [h6] by ...[Ng4].} 13. h5 b4 14. axb4 Ng4 {A nice intermediate move which gives Black a very good game.} 15. Qd2 (15. Qf4 Ne5 $1 {is only trouble for White, with the black knights targeting [c2] and [d3].}) 15... Rxb4 {[%csl Gb2][%cal Gb4b2] White's attack hasn't led anywhere, and they have to think about defending.} *

