{doesn't work either.} Bc4 $1 {White can't castle and will lose the bishop on [e4] anyway.}) 13... Nxf3+ 14. Qxf3 Bd5+ {[%cal Gd5a8,Ge7e1] Eventually getting back the knight on [a8].} *

